{"tid":1423313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於811港島東路線一問","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:58:31.000Z","uid":36844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3254d816c342279a1d054dcea7627e27f294f74","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"最近小弟係屋企group日屌夜屌<br />\n屌到屋企班港豬終於捨得出嚟行<br />\n今朝佢地wtsapp同得講筲箕灣條路就係811遊行嗰條路<br />\n但我記得811應該係維園起身然後行去北角<br />\n而家消息有啲亂，我又怕屋企人收錯風我自己又收錯風<br />\n想上嚟睇睇到底而家條路線係點<br />\n<br />\nBTW 811係我生日，十九幾個屋企人肯出嚟遊行真係我最大份生日禮物，多謝屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1ba7825cdc83dc6a260239d98bb2565d146821","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0981e4d73e874b5c066d958d6ac92a45dbb397df","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2070c65c599f0e16ed61157b360808a101175626","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"69e2ed32fd89177eebfcf0cc965ed7fbec6b9da5","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7e246f7497bd6c8fe05956331bc3f9a24fe8340d","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"abe5a9e03b851cc56bd0d536d96b91b70469c96c","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"235455ce1679af2dd679617dfe50d540dce3aa45","tid":1423313,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9a21e1195ee45bc181478aa55a7dfc49b0da1b0","tid":1423313,"uid":106523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:58:31.000Z"